| **P1** | **Disable Ruby DRb** | 1. Stop the Ruby DRb service on **Port 8787**.<br>2. If required, restrict binding to localhost and implement authentication.<br>3. Address CVE-2011-2421. | `systemctl`, Ruby Config | 1 hr | **High** |

